video_title: Elliot shares how he wasn't sure he could continue #elliotpage #struggle #keepgoing
transcript:
I I just do feel like for very
significant periods of my life I
struggled to function on a pretty basic
level you know it was hard for me to
just literally sit down it was hard for
me to be productive it was hard for me
to be you know present at all and so the
future I think I couldn't see it because
I didn't know how much longer I'd last
feeling that way in my day-to-day life
